<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Deposit Payment Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2d3748;
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9568b0 0%, #7a5294 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grain" width="100" height="100" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="50" cy="50" r="1" fill="white" opacity="0.1"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grain)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 18px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 50px 40px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(72, 187, 120, 0.3);
        }
        
        .greeting {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }
        
        .greeting h2 {
            color: #9568b0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .greeting p {
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .payment-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #f1f3f4 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #48bb78;
            padding: 35px;
            margin: 35px 0;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .payment-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(72, 187, 120, 0.05) 0%, rgba(72, 187, 120, 0.02) 100%);
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
        }
        
        .payment-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .payment-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid rgba(72, 187, 120, 0.2);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .payment-label {
            color: #718096;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .payment-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .deposit-amount {
            color: #48bb78;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .remaining-amount {
            color: #f56565;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .info-section {
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            min-width: 140px;
            color: #718096;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #f1f3f4 100%);
            padding: 35px;
            margin: 35px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .next-steps::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(149, 104, 176, 0.05) 0%, rgba(149, 104, 176, 0.02) 100%);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #9568b0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .steps-list li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-left: 35px;
            position: relative;
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .steps-list li:before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            color: #48bb78;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            background: rgba(72, 187, 120, 0.1);
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .balance-reminder {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f5 0%, #fed7d7 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #f56565;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 35px 0;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
        }
        
        .balance-reminder h4 {
            color: #c53030;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .balance-reminder p {
            color: #c53030;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #f1f3f4 100%);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .footer .highlight {
            color: #9568b0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .footer .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 40px 25px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 35px 25px;
            }
            
            .payment-section {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            .info-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding: 12px 0;
            }
            
            .info-label {
                min-width: auto;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }
            
            .next-steps {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            .footer {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Deposit Payment Confirmed</h1>
            <p>Your deposit has been successfully processed</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">Payment Successful</div>
            
            <div class="greeting">
                <h2>Hello {{customerName}},</h2>
                <p>Excellent! Your deposit payment has been successfully processed. Your move is now confirmed and we're excited to help make your relocation smooth and stress-free.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="payment-section">
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Deposit Paid:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value deposit-amount">£{{depositAmount}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Total Amount:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value">£{{totalAmount}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-row">
                    <span class="payment-label">Remaining Balance:</span>
                    <span class="payment-value remaining-amount">£{{remainingAmount}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Quote Reference:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">#{{quoteReference}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Payment Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{paymentDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Payment Time:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{paymentTime}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>We'll contact you within 24 hours to confirm your moving details</li>
                    <li>Your move date and time will be finalized</li>
                    <li>You'll receive a reminder 48 hours before your move</li>
                    <li>Remaining balance will be due on the day of your move</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="balance-reminder">
                <h4>Important: Remaining Balance</h4>
                <p>Your remaining balance of £{{remainingAmount}} will be due on the day of your move. Please ensure you have the payment method ready for the final payment.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #4a5568; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">If you need to make any changes to your booking or have questions about your move, please contact us as soon as possible. Changes made within 48 hours of your move may incur additional charges.</p>
            
            <p style="color: #9568b0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 25px;">Thank you for choosing Tranzr Moves!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="highlight">Tranzr Moves</span> - Professional moving services across the United Kingdom</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Email: support@tranzrmoves.com | Phone: +44 (0) 20 1234 5678</p>
                <p>© {{currentYear}} Tranzr Moves. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
